        We need some banner ads for the media buy we'll be doing to promote NLC on sites like coinmarketcap.com, coincap.com, coingecko.com, etc
        Submissions will be voted on by the community using the :nolimit: emoji. Winner will get 28,500 NLC2 from @dan
        How To Enter - There are 2 banner sizes needed. Please submit 1 of each size. Submit your entries in the #designcontest channel. The following are the dimensions we need:
        728x90
        160x600
        Winner will be selected as the banners with the most :nolimit: votes on it
